  "name": "app",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "next dev --port $(microfrontends port)",
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@vercel/microfrontends": "2.3.2",
    "next": "^15.0.0",
    "react": "^19.0.0",
    "react-dom": "^19.0.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "^22.0.0",
    "@types/react": "^19.0.0",
    "@types/react-dom": "^19.0.0",
    "typescript": "^5.0.0"
  }
}
```

## `apps/www/package.json`

```json
{
  "name": "www",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "next dev --port $(microfrontends port)",
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@vercel/microfrontends": "2.3.2",
    "next": "^15.0.0",
    "react": "^19.0.0",
    "react-dom": "^19.0.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "^22.0.0",
    "@types/react": "^19.0.0",
    "@types/react-dom": "^19.0.0",
    "typescript": "^5.0.0"
  }
}
```

## `apps/app/microfrontends.json`

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://openapi.vercel.sh/microfrontends.json",
  "applications": {
    "app": {
      "development": {
        "local": 4107,
        "fallback": "app.localhost"
      }
    },
    "www": {
      "development": {
        "local": 4101
      },
      "routing": [
        {
          "paths": ["/docs", "/docs/:path*"]
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

## `turbo.json`

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://turbo.build/schema.json",
  "tasks": {
    "dev": {
      "cache": false,
      "persistent": true
    },
    "typecheck": {
      "cache": false
    }
  }
}
```

Sandbox is at `/tmp/mfe-sandbox/`. Note `fallback: "app.localhost"` was required by the v2.3.2 schema validator (the default app needs a `fallback` to disambiguate from a child) — I used a placeholder hostname since no real fallback applies in this sandbox.

